    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take photos and document the world's most elusive legends, including Bigfoot, Dracula and the Loch Ness Monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a once-in-a-lifetime encounter with Bigfoot, you find yourself drawn into a deeper mystery. Chasing a lead to the Bermuda Triangle, you run aground on an uncharted island - a refuge for mythical and legendary creatures. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore Enchanting Biomes</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/589099be36b9b5799b28dcd0ec59f49e.poster.avif?t=1739411524\" width=800 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/589099be36b9b5799b28dcd0ec59f49e.webm?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/589099be36b9b5799b28dcd0ec59f49e.mp4?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through vibrant and magical landscapes, each with its own surprises. From rugged coastlines to snowy mountain peaks, and from castle-dotted lochs to mysterious forests—new creatures and secrets await you at every turn.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Capture the Perfect Photo</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/4d8ce8078329014b31e56bcc444562a1.poster.avif?t=1739411524\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/4d8ce8078329014b31e56bcc444562a1.webm?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/4d8ce8078329014b31e56bcc444562a1.mp4?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Every photo is graded on its quality, with top-tier shots earning more and unlocking new content. Capture creatures in rare moments and unique poses for even greater value! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Complete Your Creature Compendium</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/6dbe12b73452cd030836da9a64dfe0bc.poster.avif?t=1739411524\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/6dbe12b73452cd030836da9a64dfe0bc.webm?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/6dbe12b73452cd030836da9a64dfe0bc.mp4?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Fill your compendium with your most prized Polaroids, documenting each legendary creature you discover.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock New Gadgets</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/bc62f4b6efffd333eb73b86e81dde916.poster.avif?t=1739411524\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/bc62f4b6efffd333eb73b86e81dde916.webm?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148950/extras/bc62f4b6efffd333eb73b86e81dde916.mp4?t=1739411524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gain access to tools that interact with the world around you. These gadgets help you uncover hidden paths, provoke rare behaviors in creatures, and enhance your exploration. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unravel the Mystery of the Bermuda Triangle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why do vehicles vanish in the Bermuda Triangle? Why have the world’s most elusive creatures found refuge there? As a daring explorer and photographer, it’s up to you to solve this age-old mystery. </p>",
